===Noun===
{{en-noun|~|es}}

# {{label|en|agriculture|horticulture}} Any material used to cover the top [[layer]] of [[soil]] to protect, insulate, or decorate it, or to discourage [[weed]]s or retain [[moisture]].
#: ''An organic '''mulch''' is a '''mulch''' made of natural substances such as leaves or grass clippings.''
# {{label|en|countable|agriculture}} A material used as mulch, as ''a decorative redwood bark mulch.''

